pipeline.name: Test Migration Pipeline
pipeline.yaml:
pipeline:
  orgIdentifier: test-migration-org
  projectIdentifier: test-migration-project
  identifier: test-migration-pipeline
  name: Test Migration Pipeline
  stages:
    - stage:
        identifier: stage1
        name: stage1
        type: CI
        spec:
          execution:
            steps:
              - step:
                  identifier: step1
                  name: step1
                  type: Run
                  spec:
                    command: echo 'Hello from test pipeline'

template.name: Test Migration Template
template.yaml:
template:
  orgIdentifier: test-migration-org
  projectIdentifier: test-migration-project
  identifier: test-migration-template
  name: Test Migration Template
  versionLabel: v1
  type: Step
  spec:
    type: ShellScript
    spec:
      shell: Bash
      onDelegate: true
      source:
        type: Inline
        spec:
          script: echo 'Hello from test template'
